trans-unit.source: The location of an XML node in a file.
trans-unit.target: Plasseringen av en XML-node i en fil.

trans-unit.source: Any editing of the project XML through the MSBuild API's will invalidate locations in that XML until the XML is reloaded.
trans-unit.target: Redigering av prosjektet XML gjennom MSBuild-APIen blir plasseringene i dette XML til XML-filen er lastet inn på nytt.

trans-unit.source: This object is IMMUTABLE, so that it can be passed around arbitrarily.
trans-unit.target: Dette objektet er IMMUTABLE, slik at den kan bli sendt tilfeldige.

trans-unit.source: DO NOT make these objects any larger.
There are huge numbers of them and they are transmitted between nodes.
trans-unit.target: Det er stort antall dem, og de sendes mellom noder.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Construction.ElementLocation"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="Microsoft.Build.Construction.ElementLocation"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The column number where this element exists in its file.
trans-unit.target: Kolonnenummer der dette elementet finnes i en fil.

trans-unit.source: The first column is numbered 1.
Zero indicates "unknown location".
Returns <xref:System.Int32>.
Override Equals so that identical fields imply equal objects.
trans-unit.target: Overstyre lik slik at identiske felt angir lik objekter.

trans-unit.source: The element location to compare to this element location.
trans-unit.target: Elementplassering til å sammenligne på denne plasseringen for elementet.

trans-unit.source: Returns <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the objects are equal; otherwise, returns <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref> Hvis objekter er like, ellers, returnerer <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: The file from which this particular element originated.
It may differ from the ProjectFile if, for instance, it was part of an import or originated in a targets file.
trans-unit.target: Det kan være forskjellig fra ProjectFile Hvis for eksempel den var en del av en import eller kommer i en mål-fil.

trans-unit.source: If not known, returns empty string.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du ikke vet, tom returnerer streng.

trans-unit.source: Returns <xref:System.String>.
Get reasonable hash code.
Returns <xref:System.Int32>.
The line number where this element exists in its file.
trans-unit.target: Linjenummeret der dette elementet finnes i en fil.

trans-unit.source: The first line is numbered 1.
Zero indicates "unknown location".
Returns <xref:System.Int32>.
Returns <xref:System.String>.
Location of element.
Returns <xref:System.String>.
